<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l20">brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd wiſſen <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nicht / dann daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Rate her cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l22">die Jren gevertiget vnd den <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als 
